{"tid":1994613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提防人血 賤種神棍Iamgay收皮後再復出","createTime":"2020-04-29T15:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T22:37:25.000Z","uid":183576,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55a0f0c403201a652d3873d3667e04af0c6e6b39","tid":1994613,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"點睇cc台法師比人踢爆食人血饅頭？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780348</a><br />\n<br />\n人血饅頭詳細資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://buzznews.news/10336/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuzznews.news%2F10336%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=1ff73345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://buzznews.news/10336/</a><br />\n<br />\n神棍IamGay收皮瘋狂慶祝區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780360</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2k278Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2k278Z.png&h=7b85c5cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢條友舊年831後開始故弄玄虛不斷用術數風水之類無法fc嘅玄學野引導手足調查，會員知更鳥(#6845)等人出發往相關地點後再無音訊，重返連登後變左第二個人咁，絕口不提香園圍一事<br />\n知更鳥現實朋友亦表示至今未能聯絡知更鳥本人<br />\n<br />\n柚木巴打2.0 知更鳥去完香園圍疑似變左另外一個人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654353</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條賤畜之前已經自稱法師、預言家同亞特蘭提斯等人不斷散播迷信言論浪費連登版面、引導手足查一啲永遠無法fc嘅野，仲害死左幾個行動力強嘅巴絲，又食人血饅頭呃飯劵，行徑卑劣堪比APS之流，根本稱唔上同路人<br />\n佢呢幾日改左名做Bigjerpeople復出做毛，請大家一定要小心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再比呢條害死手足嘅仆街迷惑</span>"},{"pid":"2333dc48fedb83b2550e0dcdf648e6f645087b88","tid":1994613,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"嗰時佢等到凌晨34點先岀post ,普通人見唔到，但係啲信徒就日日follow"},{"pid":"19c3010924677340482aecd03a93a941f8047714","tid":1994613,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T